{"title":"南瓜与红米","authors":["肖韶光"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":7,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南瓜与红米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖韶光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这片土地神奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年乡亲泪滴成瓣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结出带瓣的南瓜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒下热血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获红米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山伢仔插根梭标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长出红缨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种下一颗星火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆出漫山红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南瓜与红米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝红土地灵气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要脚下有片泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就挺直腰板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耐寒耐苦耐清贫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傲血雨腥风不移"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当革命在摇篮里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥渴得喘息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好在有了南瓜红米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熬着清淡粗糙的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相濡以沫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与一个阶级的命运维系"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为挨打的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酿造阳刚之气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了南瓜红米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命就站稳了根据地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南瓜花昂起进击的号角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红米的谷穗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"构成待发的金弓铜镝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那根著名的竹扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一头镌刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《井冈山的斗争》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一头载着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"元帅与士兵挑粮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和“南瓜生蛋”＊的传奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦红米饭南瓜汤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一首歌谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一种底蕴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为华夏的脊梁补钙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将偌大的中国撑起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红米饭啊南瓜汤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耐几代人寻味与回味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华民族的那段岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如不是南瓜与红米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们可能还要天天吃着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南瓜与红米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊根据地群众巧妙地将鸡蛋装进掏空了瓜瓤的南瓜送来慰劳红军，红军始料不及，因而有了“南瓜生蛋”的传奇故事，流传至今。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}